<PB REF="1" MS="y">
<P>THE DOCTOR AND THE APOTHECARY. A MUSICAL ENTERTAINMENT IN TWO ACTS. AS PERFORMED AT THE THEATRE-ROYAL, DRURY-LANE.</P>
<P>LONDON: PRINTED FOR C. DILLY, IN THE POULTRY. MDCCLXXXVIII.</P>
</DIV1>
<DIV1 TYPE="dramatis personae">
<PB REF="2">
<HEAD>DRAMATIS PERSONAE.</HEAD>
<LIST>
<LABEL>THOMASO,</LABEL>
<ITEM>MR. PARSONS.</ITEM>
<LABEL>STURMWALD&punc;</LABEL>
<ITEM>MR. DODD.</ITEM>
<LABEL>CARLOS,</LABEL>
<ITEM>MR. KELLY.</ITEM>
<LABEL>JUAN,</LABEL>
<ITEM>MR. BANNISTER, JUN&punc;</ITEM>
<LABEL>GUZMAN,</LABEL>
<ITEM>MR. SEDGWICK.</ITEM>
<LABEL>DR. BILIOSO,</LABEL>
<ITEM>MR. SUETT.</ITEM>
<LABEL>PEREZ,</LABEL>
<ITEM>MR. BURTON.</ITEM>
<LABEL>ANNA,</LABEL>
<ITEM>MRS. CROUCH.</ITEM>
<LABEL>ISABELLA,</LABEL>
<ITEM>MISS ROMANZINI.</ITEM>
<LABEL>THERESA,</LABEL>
<ITEM>MRS. BOOTH.</ITEM>
</LIST>
